      </ns-card>
    </div>
  </ns-column>
  <ns-column hockeypitch="2:1">
    <div>
      <h4>Further reading</h4>
      <dl class="dl-stack">
        <div>
          <dt><a href="#!">Using your smart energy monitor</a>
          </dt>
          <dd>Your smart energy monitor can help you save energy and money, so find out how to use it and read your energy's display device.</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt><a href="#!">Using pay as you go meters in your new home</a>
          <dd>If your new home has a pay as you go meter, you can find out everything you need to know about your British Gas prepayment meter here.
